HEADWORD: Arrose
<hw>Ar*rose"</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>arroser</ets>.]</ety> <def>To drench; to besprinkle; to
moisten.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The blissful dew of heaven does <qex>arrose</qex> you.</q>
<rj><qau>Two N. Kins.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Arrosion</ent>⟦br⟧
